===============
Flask-Vue
===============
.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/Flask-Vue.svg
    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/Flask-Vue/
.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/dm/Flask-Vue.svg
